title: South Australia records first coronavirus death
description: South Australia records its first death from COVID–19, with a man in his 70s dying at the Royal Adelaide Hospital overnight.
content:
Updated 
April 07, 2020 09:04:37
South Australia has recorded its first death from COVID19, with a man in his 70s dying at the Royal Adelaide Hospital overnight.
